1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,991
Welcome to Safe Place Visualization for
Your Inner Child.

2
00:00:05,991 --> 00:00:13,530
This practice invites you to create an
inner place where a younger part of you

3
00:00:13,530 --> 00:00:17,740
can feel protected, welcomed, and
unhurried.

4
00:00:17,740 --> 00:00:20,851
You do not need to force an image.

5
00:00:20,851 --> 00:00:28,653
You can sense, imagine, or simply choose
the idea of a safe place.

6
00:00:40,653 --> 00:00:40,653
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

7
00:00:40,653 --> 00:00:44,415
Begin by settling into your body.

8
00:00:44,415 --> 00:00:47,852
Feel the surface underneath you.

9
00:00:47,852 --> 00:00:50,546
Notice the room around you.

10
00:00:59,546 --> 00:00:59,546
<break time="3s" />

11
00:00:59,546 --> 00:01:02,193
Take a slow breath in.

12
00:01:11,193 --> 00:01:11,193
<break time="3s" />

13
00:01:11,193 --> 00:01:13,747
And let it out.

14
00:01:13,747 --> 00:01:19,831
Now imagine a place that could feel safe
for a younger part of you.

15
00:01:31,831 --> 00:01:31,831
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

16
00:01:31,831 --> 00:01:39,492
It may be real or imaginary. It may be
indoors or outdoors. It may be simple or

17
00:01:39,492 --> 00:01:40,376
detailed.

18
00:01:40,376 --> 00:01:50,163
Maybe a cozy room, a treehouse, a garden,
a beach, a cabin, a soft blanket fort, a

19
00:01:50,163 --> 00:01:54,029
quiet library, or a sunny porch.

20
00:01:54,029 --> 00:01:57,094
Let the place form slowly.

21
00:01:57,094 --> 00:02:06,939
Notice the colors. The light. The
temperature. The textures. The sounds.

22
00:02:06,939 --> 00:02:09,958
Notice what makes this place feel safe.

23
00:02:09,958 --> 00:02:15,113
Now imagine adding whatever this younger
part might need.

24
00:02:27,113 --> 00:02:27,113
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

25
00:02:27,113 --> 00:02:34,739
A soft chair. A blanket. A favorite toy.
A pet. A protective door. A window with

26
00:02:34,739 --> 00:02:40,627
warm light. Art supplies. Music. Space to
move. Space to hide.

27
00:02:40,627 --> 00:02:43,738
Let the place become supportive.

28
00:02:43,738 --> 00:02:52,241
Now ask inside: Is there a younger part
of me that would like to visit this safe

29
00:02:52,241 --> 00:02:52,887
place?

30
00:03:04,887 --> 00:03:04,887
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

31
00:03:04,887 --> 00:03:12,410
If no part appears, that is okay. The
place can be prepared for later.

32
00:03:12,410 --> 00:03:19,004
If a younger part appears, notice how
close or far away they are.

33
00:03:37,004 --> 00:03:37,004
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

34
00:03:37,004 --> 00:03:44,344
Ask gently: Would you like to come
closer, stay where you are, or just look

35
00:03:44,344 --> 00:03:47,221
at the place from a distance?

36
00:03:59,221 --> 00:03:59,221
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

37
00:03:59,221 --> 00:04:01,729
Respect the answer.

38
00:04:01,729 --> 00:04:06,094
This place does not demand anything.

39
00:04:06,094 --> 00:04:13,432
Now ask the younger part: What would help
this place feel safer for you?

40
00:04:25,432 --> 00:04:25,432
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

41
00:04:25,432 --> 00:04:30,748
Maybe they want someone trustworthy
nearby. Maybe they want a locked door.

42
00:04:30,748 --> 00:04:36,647
Maybe they want softness. Maybe they want
brightness. Maybe they want quiet. Maybe

43
00:04:36,647 --> 00:04:37,739
they want play.

44
00:04:37,739 --> 00:04:41,501
Imagine adding what feels welcome.

45
00:04:53,501 --> 00:04:53,501
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

46
00:04:53,501 --> 00:04:58,702
Now ask: Where would you like to be in
this place?

47
00:05:10,702 --> 00:05:10,702
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

48
00:05:10,702 --> 00:05:13,024
Let the part choose.

49
00:05:13,024 --> 00:05:22,498
They may sit, stand, hide, explore, play,
or simply watch.

50
00:05:22,498 --> 00:05:25,702
You do not need to direct them.

51
00:05:25,702 --> 00:05:29,557
Now offer a message from Self-energy.

52
00:05:29,557 --> 00:05:35,398
You might say: This place is for you. You
do not have to perform here. You do not

53
00:05:35,398 --> 00:05:41,240
have to explain everything. You can come
here when you need rest. You are allowed

54
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,189
to go slowly.

55
00:05:51,189 --> 00:05:51,189
<break time="3s" />

56
00:05:51,189 --> 00:05:54,626
Notice how the younger part responds.

57
00:06:12,626 --> 00:06:12,626
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

58
00:06:12,626 --> 00:06:18,059
Now imagine a protective boundary around
the safe place.

59
00:06:30,059 --> 00:06:30,059
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

60
00:06:30,059 --> 00:06:33,960
Only supportive energy is allowed in.

61
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:38,186
Only what this part consents to can
enter.

62
00:06:38,186 --> 00:06:41,901
The younger part can decide who comes
close.

63
00:06:41,901 --> 00:06:47,520
Now ask: Is there anything you want me to
remember about this place?

64
00:06:59,520 --> 00:06:59,520
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

65
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:00,635
Listen.

66
00:07:18,635 --> 00:07:18,635
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

67
00:07:18,635 --> 00:07:26,344
Now let the younger part know that this
safe place remains available.

68
00:07:26,344 --> 00:07:33,638
They can return here in future practices.
They can adjust it. They can change it.

69
00:07:33,638 --> 00:07:36,282
They can make it more theirs.

70
00:07:36,282 --> 00:07:40,276
Thank the younger part for any contact it
allowed.

71
00:07:40,276 --> 00:07:44,363
Thank your system for creating a place of
care.

72
00:07:44,363 --> 00:07:48,543
Now slowly return attention to your adult
body.

73
00:07:48,543 --> 00:07:50,958
Feel your breath.

74
00:07:50,958 --> 00:07:53,141
Feel your hands.

75
00:07:53,141 --> 00:07:55,370
Feel your feet.

76
00:08:04,370 --> 00:08:04,370
<break time="3s" />

77
00:08:04,370 --> 00:08:06,228
Notice the room.

78
00:08:15,228 --> 00:08:15,228
<break time="3s" />

79
00:08:15,228 --> 00:08:18,014
Take a slow breath in.

80
00:08:27,014 --> 00:08:27,014
<break time="3s" />

81
00:08:27,014 --> 00:08:28,732
And let it out.

82
00:08:28,732 --> 00:08:31,518
When you are ready, return.

